e="soccerway">{{cite web|url=https://int.soccerway.com/players/cameron-humphries/376291/|title=England – C. Humphreys – Profile with news, career statistics and history – Soccerway|publisher=soccerway.com|accessdate=2016-01-30}}</ref>
==Club career== Humphreys is a graduate of the youth system at [[Manchester City F.C|Manchester City]]. In the summer of 2015, a 16 year old Humphreys travelled with the first team squad on their preseason tour and played in a friendly fixture against Real Madrid.<ref>{{cite news|author= |url=http://www.manchestereveningnews.co.uk/sport/football/football-news/manchester-city-cristiano-cameron-humphreys-10837236 |title=Manchester City: Cristiano Ronaldo doesn't faze Cameron Humphreys – but not much does! |newspaper=[[Manchester Evening News]] |date=2016-02-05 |accessdate=2016-02-22}}</ref> Humphreys signed his first professional contract on 24 August, two days after his 17th birthday.<ref>{{cite news|author= |url=http://www.manchestereveningnews.co.uk/sport/football/football-news/man-city-jason-wilcox-proud-9851712 |title=Man City: Jason Wilcox proud of Humphreys and Garcia |newspaper=[[Manchester Evening News]] |date=2015-08-24 |accessdate=2016-02-22}}</ref> On 30 January 2016, he made his competitive debut in a [[FA Cup]] game against [[Aston Villa F.C.|Aston Villa]]. He replaced [[Nicolás Otamendi]] after 88 minutes in a 4–0 victory at [[Villa Park]].<ref name="soccerway2">{{cite web|url=https://int.soccerway.com/matches/2016/01/30/england/fa-cup/aston-villa-football-club/manchester-city-football-club/2185964/|title=Aston Villa vs. Liverpool – 30 January 2016 – Soccerway|publisher=soccerway.com|accessdate=2016-01-30}}</ref> Humphreys is now a key member of both the Premier League 2 and UEFA Youth League sides at [[Manchester City F.C|Manchester City]].<ref>{{cite web |title=Cameron Humphreys' official Manchester City FC profile page |url=https://www.mancity.com/cameron-humphreys |publisher=[[Manchester City FC]] |accessdate= 9 February 2017}}</ref>
==International career== Humphreys has represented England up to U19 level, making his debut for England U17 as a 14 year old.<ref>{{cite web|last=Flanagan |first=Aaron |url=https://www.mirror.co.uk/sport/football/news/who-cameron-humphreys-man-citys-6129287 |title=Who is Cameron Humphreys? Man City's 16-year-old defender given baptism of fire against Ronaldo, Benzema and co – Mirror Online |website=Mirror.co.uk |date=2015-07-24 |accessdate=2016-02-22}}</ref>
